                            VitalCare is a multispecialty medical company that integrates medical specialties,
                            comprehensive dental care, diagnostic laboratories and pharmaceuticals.
                            Our story begins from October of 2011. Back then we were a clinic with a single dental unit in the capital city of Male’.
                            Vitalcare was established by doctors with a dream of advancing quality healthcare, and to help ensure that people’s health is protected
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <div class="row">
                    <ul class="nav nav-pills gap-2  d-flex justify-content-center" id="pills-tab" role="tablist">
